Fig. 24
). Uterus with 14-25 lateral diverticula on each side (
Figs 24, 25
). Eggs oval, outer envelope 21-25 × 18-19, bilayered embryophore 19-20 × 13-15, oncosphere 9-10 × 11-12, embryonic hooks 5-6 long (
